# Expo Continuous Native Generation — native projects at the mobile/
# root are regenerated via `npx expo prebuild`, not committed. The
# leading slash anchors the pattern so modules/*/ios and modules/*/android
# (where our Expo-Modul-Wrapper lives) bleiben tracked.
